item.title: Imperial leave it late to snatch victory against Hult
item.author: Philipp M Gerstenberg,
item.description: Last Saturday IC 7s faced off against Hult International Business School 2s in Victoria Park. The day got off to a bad start when Giles Wane decided he would miss the meeting time altogether after his alarm just decided it would not go off that morning.
